"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkj22tdEctDI&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a71d4d77\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kj22tdEctDI</a><br />\n頭盔：有機會開壞個鎖</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打意見 不過我附近毛都無條 要出好遠先有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有焗住揾開鎖佬 開鎖大概要幾錢到？</blockquote><br />\n你預今日應該開鎖3-4舊 換埋大概夾埋8舊-1叉野到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 無壞鎖係咪都一定要成個換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢D鎖佢地多數會搵百合匙試 你呢款鎖成功率你預2-3成到<br />\n如果真係開唔到就應該會爆 爆咪要成個換囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5805859220fbead074bbef02d5ead953d12b6510","tid":224711,"uid":21120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無電話點開po?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我幾時有話過我無電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企人唔喺香港 頭先落一落會所點知無帶鎖匙...<br />\n跪求將軍澳區嘅開鎖佬<br />\nor有無巴絲識開鎖...<br />\n好緊急因爲<span style=\"color: red;\">除左銀包同電話咩都喺哂入面</span><br />\n屋企仲有隻狗 <br />\n希望有人可以幫到手 薄酬  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa7c26602c9966c2fb2351078bfd91e03fe79a3","tid":224711,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"換把電子帶卡咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52641e2c85c989a17f1cb25b0cdbf0bd4d259d17","tid":224711,"uid":112571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無電話點開po?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkg